"Change Set:		9824Collections-ul.349Collections-ul.349:- use the TextConverter's to encode/decode strings"!!ByteString methodsFor: 'converting' stamp: 'ul 3/26/2010 23:30'!squeakToUtf8	"Convert the given string (self) to UTF-8 from Squeak's internal representation."	^UTF8TextConverter encodeByteString: self! !!ByteString methodsFor: 'converting' stamp: 'ul 3/26/2010 23:29'!utf8ToSqueak	"Convert the given string (self) from UTF-8 to Squeak's internal representation."		^UTF8TextConverter decodeByteString: self! !!String methodsFor: 'converting' stamp: 'ul 3/13/2010 19:43'!convertToWithConverter: converter 	^(converter ifNil: [ ^self]) encodeString: self! !!String methodsFor: 'converting' stamp: 'ul 3/13/2010 19:43'!convertFromWithConverter: converter	^(converter ifNil: [ ^self]) decodeString: self! !